'''Lindissë''' was the first child and only daughter of [[Axantur]], a nobleman of [[Númenor]]. Her great-nephew [[Hallacar]] would marry [[Tar-Ancalimë]], the first [[Ruling Queen of Númenor]]. Almost nothing is known about her life.<ref>{{UT|earlier}}</ref>

==Etymology==
''Lindissë'' is a [[Quenya]] name. Its meaning is not glossed, but Paul Strack suggests it means "Singer" and is a compound of ''[[lind]]ë'' ("singing", "song", "musical sound") and the feminine suffix ''[[-issë]]'' (ending in feminine names).<ref>{{webcite|author=Paul Strack|articleurl=https://www.eldamo.org/content/words/word-1239695017.html|articlename=Q. ''Lindissë'' f.|website=Eldamo|accessed=21 January 2022}}</ref>

